properties.SQL Query:
SELECT transaction_id, date_key, product_id, store_id, customer_sk,
quantity, total_amount FROM ( SELECT * FROM staging.raw_transaction WHERE
transaction_id NOT IN ( SELECT transaction_id FROM staging.data_issue ) AND
transaction_id NOT IN ( SELECT transaction_id FROM fact_sales ) ) AS T JOIN
dim_date ON transaction_date = full_date JOIN dim_customer C ON T.customer_id
= C.customer_id AND T.transaction_date BETWEEN valid_from AND valid_to

properties.Success:
SELECT *, CASE WHEN LEAD(transaction_date) OVER (
PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY transaction_date ) IS NOT NULL
THEN LEAD(transaction_date) OVER ( PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER
BY transaction_date ) - 1 ELSE '9999-12-31' END AS valid_to FROM
FLOWFILE

properties.previous:
SELECT customer_sk, TIMESTAMPADD(DAY, -1,
CAST(MIN(transaction_date) AS DATE)) AS valid_to FROM FLOWFILE
WHERE transaction_date > valid_from AND city <> current_city GROUP BY
customer_sk
properties.nothing:
SELECT 1 FROM FLOWFILE WHERE transaction_date <= valid_from
OR city = current_city
properties.changed:
SELECT customer_id, name, gender, birth_date, city, customer_type,
transaction_date FROM FLOWFILE WHERE transaction_date > valid_from AND
city <> current_city

properties.dim_customer:
SELECT customer_id, name, gender, birth_date, city,
customer_type, transaction_date FROM ( SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
PARTITION BY customer_id, name, gender, birth_date, city, customer_type
ORDER BY transaction_id ) AS rn FROM FLOWFILE ) WHERE rn = 1
